ice| last3=Teroni| title=In Defense of Shame: The Faces of an Emotion| publisher=Oxford University Press| year=2012| isbn=9780199793532| url=https://books.google.com/books/about/In_Defense_of_Shame.html?id=EmEQb13xm9IC| ref=harv}}\n\n*{{cite book| last=Dundas| first=Paul| year=2004| title=The Jains| location=London| publisher=Routledge| doi=10.4324/9780203398272| isbn=9780203398272| ref=harv}}\n\n*{{cite book| last=Fagan| first=Garrett G.| year=2002| title=Bathing in Public in the Roman World| publisher=University of Michigan Press| url=https://books.google.com/?id=R6tz_TzSVkAC&pg=PA1#v=onepage&q&f=false |ref=harv| isbn=0472088653}}\n\n*{{cite book| edition = 3rd| publisher = Gale| volume = 2| pages = 1642\u20131644| editor-first = Kristin | editor-last=Key| last1 = Fallon| first1 = L. Fleming| last2 = Davidson| first2 = Tish| title = The Gale Encyclopedia of Mental Health| chapter = Voyeurism| location = Detroit, MI| date = 2012|ref=harv}}\n\n*{{cite book| first1=Rebecca| last1=Frey| first2=Emily Jane| last2=Willingham| chapter=Exhibitionism| title=The Gale Encyclopedia of Mental Health| edition=3rd |editor-first = Kristin | editor-last=Key| pages=598-602| volume=1| location=Detroit, MI| publisher=Gale| year=2012| ref=harv}}\n\n*{{cite book| last=Goldman| first=Leslie| title=Locker Room Diaries : The Naked Truth about Women, Body Image, and Re-imagining the \"Perfect\" Body| publisher=Da Capo Press| location=Cambridge, MA| year=2007| isbn=9786612788604 |ref=harv}}\n\n*{{cite book|last1= Gordon |first1=Betty N. |last2=Schroeder |first2=Carolyn S. |year=1995 |title=Sexuality: A Developmental Approach to Problems |publisher=Springer |isbn=978-0-306-45040-2| ref=harv}}\n\n*{{cite book| last=G\u00f3rnicka| first=Barbara| year=2016| chapter=From Lewd to Nude: Becoming a Naturist| title=Nakedness, Shame, and Embarrassment| series=Figurationen. Schriften zur Zivilisations und Prozesstheorie| volume=12| publisher=Springer VS| location=Wiesbaden| ref=harv}}\n\n*{{cite book |