{"title_page": "Tolstukha", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n|official_name          = Tolstukha\n|other_name             = \n|native_name            = \u0422\u043e\u043b\u0441\u0442\u0443\u0445\u0430\n|nickname               = \n|settlement_type        = Village\n|image_skyline          = \n|image_caption          = \n|pushpin_map            = Russia Vologda Oblast#Russia\n|pushpin_label_position = \n|pushpin_mapsize        =\n|pushpin_map_caption    = \n|subdivision_type       = Country\n|subdivision_name       = [[Russia]]\n|subdivision_type1      = [[List of regions of Russia|Region]] \n|subdivision_name1      = [[Vologda Oblast]]\n|subdivision_type2      = [[Counties of Russia|County]] \n|subdivision_name2      = \n|subdivision_type3      = [[Districts of Russia|District]] \n|subdivision_name3      = [[Verkhovazhsky District]]\n|subdivision_type4      = [[List of municipalities of Russia|Municipality]]\n|subdivision_name4      = \n|timezone1              = \n|utc_offset1            = +3:00\n|timezone1_DST          = \n|utc_offset1_DST        = \n|postal_code_type       = \n|postal_code            = \n|elevation_m            = \n|elevation_footnotes    = \n|coordinates            = {{coord|60|30|N|41|54|E|display=inline}}<ref>[https://mapdata.ru/vologodskaya-oblast/verhovazhskiy-rayon/ \u041a\u0430\u0440\u0442\u0430 \u0412\u0435\u0440\u0445\u043e\u0432\u0430\u0436\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0433\u043e \u0440\u0430\u0439\u043e\u043d\u0430 \u0412\u043e\u043b\u043e\u0433\u043e\u0434\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0439 \u043e\u0431\u043b\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0438]</ref>\n}}\n'''Tolstukha''' ({{lang-ru|\u0422\u043e\u043b\u0441\u0442\u0443\u0445\u0430}}) is a [[types of inhabited localities in Russia|rural locality]] (a [[Village#Russia|village]]) in Chushevitskoye Rural Settlement, [[Verkhovazhsky District]], [[Vologda Oblast]], Russia. The population was 3 as of 2002.<ref>\u0414\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044b\u0435 \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0435\u043f\u0438\u0441\u0438 2002 \u0433\u043e\u0434\u0430: \u0442\u0430\u0431\u043b\u0438\u0446\u0430 2\u0421. \u041c.: \u0424\u0435\u0434\u0435\u0440\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0430\u044f \u0441\u043b\u0443\u0436\u0431\u0430 \u0433\u043e\u0441\u0443\u0434\u0430\u0440\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0439 \u0441\u0442\u0430\u0442\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0438\u043a\u0438, 2004.</ref>\n\n== Geography ==\nThe distance to [[Verkhovazhye]] is 53.8 km, to Chushevits is 10 km. Vladykina Gora, Dubrova, Spirino are the nearest rural localities.\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Rural localities in Verkhovazhsky District}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Rural localities in Vologda Oblast]]\n[[Category:Rural localities in Verkhovazhsky District]]\n\n{{VologdaOblast-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|official_name          = Tolstukha\n|other_name             = \n|native_name            = \u0422\u043e\u043b\u0441\u0442\u0443\u0445\u0430\n|nickname               = \n|settlement_type        = Village\n|image_skyline          = \n|image_caption          = \n|pushpin_map            = Russia Vologda Oblast#Russia\n|pushpin_label_position = \n|pushpin_mapsize        =\n|pushpin_map_caption    = \n|subdivision_type       = Country\n|subdivision_name       = [[Russia]]\n|subdivision_type1      = [[List of regions of Russia|Region]] \n|subdivision_name1      = [[Vologda Oblast]]\n|subdivision_type2      = [[Counties of Russia|County]] \n|subdivision_name2      = \n|subdivision_type3      = [[Districts of Russia|District]] \n|subdivision_name3      = [[Verkhovazhsky District]]\n|subdivision_type4      = [[List of municipalities of Russia|Municipality]]\n|subdivision_name4      = \n|timezone1              = \n|utc_offset1            = +3:00\n|timezone1_DST          = \n|utc_offset1_DST        = \n|postal_code_type       = \n|postal_code            = \n|elevation_m            = \n|elevation_footnotes    = \n|coordinates            = {{coord|60|30|N|41|54|E|display=inline}}<ref>[https://mapdata.ru/vologodskaya-oblast/verhovazhskiy-rayon/ \u041a\u0430\u0440\u0442\u0430 \u0412\u0435\u0440\u0445\u043e\u0432\u0430\u0436\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0433\u043e \u0440\u0430\u0439\u043e\u043d\u0430 \u0412\u043e\u043b\u043e\u0433\u043e\u0434\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0439 \u043e\u0431\u043b\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0438]</ref>\n}}\n'''Tolstukha''' ({{lang-ru|\u0422\u043e\u043b\u0441\u0442\u0443\u0445\u0430}}) is a [[types of inhabited localities in Russia|rural locality]] (a [[Village#Russia|village]]) in Chushevitskoye Rural Settlement, [[Verkhovazhsky District]], [[Vologda Oblast]], Russia. The population was 3 as of 2002.<ref>\u0414\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044b\u0435 \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0435\u043f\u0438\u0441\u0438 2002 \u0433\u043e\u0434\u0430: \u0442\u0430\u0431\u043b\u0438\u0446\u0430 2\u0421. \u041c.: \u0424\u0435\u0434\u0435\u0440\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0430\u044f \u0441\u043b\u0443\u0436\u0431\u0430 \u0433\u043e\u0441\u0443\u0434\u0430\u0440\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0439 \u0441\u0442\u0430\u0442\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0438\u043a\u0438, 2004.</ref>\n\n== Geography ==\nThe distance to [[Verkhovazhye]] is 53.8 km, to Chushevits is 10 km. Vladykina Gora, Dubrova, Spirino are the nearest rural localities.\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Rural localities in Verkhovazhsky District}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Rural localities in Vologda Oblast]]\n[[Category:Rural localities in Verkhovazhsky District]]\n\n\n{{VologdaOblast-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Wagino 20100516", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:clean up", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tolstukha"}
